    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Validation evidence (VR vr-hemolysis-bench-2025) demonstrates mean RHI error of 4.2% against FDA pump bench data, well within the 10% acceptance threshold. The assessment team notes that validation runs were executed under ansys-cfx-24-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2 rather than the released build 2026-q1-build-7; vendor release notes confirm the patch addressed only a post-processing memory allocation issue with no changes to solver numerics. The team judges the rc2 results as directly applicable to the released version. On this basis the COU1 credibility assessment is Accepted.",
